<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="evil-n">evil <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'iːvl/    美 /'iːvl/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>邪恶；罪恶；坏处：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>return good for evil 
以德报怨</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Money is often said to be the root of all evil. 
人们常说金钱是万恶之源。</p></div></div>